'''NGC 3628'''，或者稱為'''漢堡星系'''（'''Hamburger Galaxy'''）<ref>{{Cite web|title = Chomp! Hamburger Galaxy Feeds Stargazer's Cosmic Appetite (Photo)|url = http://www.space.com/21914-hamburger-galaxy-stargazer-photo.html|accessdate = 2015-06-14|publisher = Space.com|date = 2013-07-28|last = Sen|first = Nina|archive-date = 2015-06-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150625014528/http://www.space.com/21914-hamburger-galaxy-stargazer-photo.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>、'''薩拉星系'''（'''Sarah's Galaxy'''）<ref name="skyandtelescope">{{cite web|url=http://www.skyandtelescope.com/sky-and-telescope-magazine/inside-march-2015-issue/|title=Inside the March 2015 Issue - Sky & Telescope|publisher=skyandtelescope.com|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924124120/http://www.skyandtelescope.com/sky-and-telescope-magazine/inside-march-2015-issue/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="annesastronomynews">{{cite web|url=http://annesastronomynews.com/photo-gallery-ii/galaxies-clusters/ngc-3628-sarahs-galaxy-is-an-unbarred-spiral-galaxy-showing-a-puffy-galactic-disk-divided-by-dark-dust-lanes-35-million-ly-away-in-leo-it-has-an-300000-ly-long-tidal-tail/|title=NGC 3628 (Sarah’s Galaxy)|publisher=annesastronomynews.com|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050942/http://annesastronomynews.com/photo-gallery-ii/galaxies-clusters/ngc-3628-sarahs-galaxy-is-an-unbarred-spiral-galaxy-showing-a-puffy-galactic-disk-divided-by-dark-dust-lanes-35-million-ly-away-in-leo-it-has-an-300000-ly-long-tidal-tail/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="astronomersdoitinthedark">{{cite web|url=http://www.astronomersdoitinthedark.com/index.php?c=121&p=454|title=Astronomers Do It In The Dark - NGC 3628 - the 3rd Galaxy in the Leo Triplet (reprocessed) - Spiral Galaxies - Typically younger galaxies with Spiral Arms of star formation|publisher=astronomersdoitinthedark.com|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304033731/http://www.astronomersdoitinthedark.com/index.php?c=121&p=454|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wordpress">{{cite web|url=https://rolandlinda3.wordpress.com/2014/05/04/the-delight-of-sarahs-galaxy/|title=The Delight of Sarah’s Galaxy | Parables of the Sky Blog|publisher=rolandlinda3.wordpress.com|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015183230/https://rolandlinda3.wordpress.com/2014/05/04/the-delight-of-sarahs-galaxy/|archive-date=2015-10-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="iac">{{cite web|url=http://www.iac.es/telescopes/IAM/2011/75-jul11-ngc-3628.jpg.html|title=Astronomy Picture of the Month | 2011 | The Sarah's Galaxy|publisher=iac.es|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924032458/http://www.iac.es/telescopes/IAM/2011/75-jul11-ngc-3628.jpg.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一個位於[[獅子座|獅子座]]的[[無棒螺旋星系|無棒螺旋星系]]，距離[[地球|地球]]3,500萬[[光年|光年]]。它於1784年由英國天文學家[[弗里德里希·威廉·赫歇爾|赫歇爾]]發現，這個星系與[[M65|M65]]和[[M66|M66]]兩個[[漩渦星系|螺旋星系]]，一同構成[[獅子座三胞胎|獅子座三胞胎]]。此外，這個星系也屬於[[電波星系|電波星系]]。

因為Ngc 3628在許多波段的影像都可見到它的核球為X型，因此有天文學家宣稱它其實是棒狀結構只有一端面對地球的[[棒旋星系|棒旋星系]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.calvin.edu/academic/phys/observatory/images/Astr212.Spring2009/Haegert.html |title=NGC 3628, Melissa J. Haegert |accessdate=2017-05-09 |archive-date=2016-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824065839/https://www.calvin.edu/academic/phys/observatory/images/Astr212.Spring2009/Haegert.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電腦模擬顯示盤狀星系的棒狀結構可形成於和其他星系的重力交互作用與合併時，而目前NGC 3628正在和另外兩個巨大的鄰近星系交互作用中。

